### 2. Hero Section (Minimal + Text-Driven)
**Headline:**
One Craftsman. One Vision. Built by Hand, Built to Last.

**Subtext:**
Custom cabinetry, built-ins, and heirloom furniture designed, built, and delivered by a single craftsman.

**CTA:**
[ Request a Quote ]

---

### 3. Value Proposition Section
**3 Columns or stacked blocks:**
- Fully Custom Work  
  Every piece designed and built specifically for you

- Direct Craftsman Experience  
  Work directly with the builder from start to finish

- Built to Last  
  Premium hardwoods and time-tested craftsmanship

---

